---
title: Creamy Pesto Pasta with Peas, Spinach and Cheese
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Creamy Pesto Pasta in just 20 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-pesto-pasta-eff713f7-bf26e21b.jpg
